Hello and welcome to Odonto.me!

If you haven't already, you can go to http://my.odonto.me
and login with your email address and password to start
setting up your practice in My practice

- You can start by customizing your settings like
  preferred language and name in My practice settings

- Add users that can access your account (say an 
  assistant) or change your first and last name (you
  are initially named 'Administrator User') in My Users

- Or add the Doctors who will see your Patients in 
  My Doctors.

Then you can start adding Patients and Appointments
from the links on the top of the page.

Please don't ever hesitate to contact us if you need
anything.


